  [warning] Misuse of `TrimLeft`
   ╭─[test.lis:6:31]
 5 │   let s = "//path"
 6 │   let _ = strings.TrimLeft(s, "//")
   ·                               ──┬─
   ·                                 ╰── treated as charset
